[SHORT DESC]
Cures freeze. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>If held by a Pokemon, will automatically cure the freeze status condition when inflicted on the holder. Consumed after use. Can also be used forcibly by the trainer in-game. Natural Gift becomes a 60 Base Power Ice-type attack when the user holds this Berry, but the Berry is consumed after use.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>The Aspear Berry is generally useless, as there is no reliable freeze move in existence. If you want protection from status, use Lum Berry, which cures every status, not just freeze.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>Dream World (Windswept Sky).</p>
<p>Studio Castelia in Castelia City - show Harlequin a Pokemon of the type he asks for.</p>